{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Avrora and Her Jovial Friends\n\n<size=45>Chapter 1: Daybreak of Victory<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Today, many light cruisers from around the port gathered to conduct a ship-class specific exercise...","dir":1,"bgm":"battle-2","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Crap! Damn it, don't tell me I've also been sunk...","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"move","y":-1000,"delay":1.2,"dur":1,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":102060},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Another team member is out... at this rate, we won't be able to hold out!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.15,"number":3,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":102090},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"D-did Akashi mess up the settings with these virtual enemies? I've never fought enemies this tough before...","actor":202110,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Sister, please focus on the enemies in front of you! Otherwise, you too will be sunk!","actor":202120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Even with their combined strength, the light cruisers were still struggling.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Ning Hai, what are we gonna do?","actor":502030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Focus on dodging! But if this keeps up...","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":502020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Don't panic, everyone!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"speed"}],"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":702010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Suddenly, the inspiring voice of the protected cruiser, Avrora, rang out across the surface of the ocean.","dir":1,"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"speed"}],"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"In our fights against the Sirens, my comrades never lost hope, even when severely outnumbered and outgunned.","actor":702010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"We shouldn't treat this exercise any differently - treat this as a life or death battle, and show your true power - the determination of a ship!","actor":702010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Heh, if Avrora's going to give us a pep talk like that...","actor":102090,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"...then we have no choice but to do our utmost. Am I correct, Lady Cleveland?","actor":202120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"You betcha! All right everyone, we're gonna take out every last one of them!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.15,"number":3,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":102090},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Ping Hai, we're pushing ahead! Follow me!","actor":502020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Got it!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.15,"number":3,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":502030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Jeez, look at them, charging forward after saying something cool...","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.1,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","actor":202110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I-I'm coming too! If everyone else is going, I can't be left behind!","actor":202110,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Hehe~ Now that's what revolutsiya looks like~","actor":702010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"After hearing Avrora's rousing words, her colleagues began to charge forward courageously, smashing through the enemy ships.","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"...By the way, Akashi really did make a mistake in the settings.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"AFULEER1","fadeOut":1.5}